		"description": "Complete authentication system with Email OTP and Google Authenticator 2FA.\n\n## Test Credentials\nAfter running the application, you can create test users using the signup flow.\n\n### Sample Test User 1:\n- Username: testuser1\n- Email: test1@example.com\n- Password: Test123!\n\n### Sample Test User 2:\n- Username: testuser2\n- Email: test2@example.com\n- Password: Test123!\n\n## Setup Instructions\n1. Start the application using Docker Compose: `docker-compose up`\n2. Use the Signup flow to create a new user\n3. Check the console logs for the OTP code\n4. Verify the signup OTP\n5. Login with the created user\n6. (Optional) Setup Google Authenticator for additional 2FA\n\n## Variables\n- base_url: http://localhost:8080\n- session_token: Will be set automatically after login",
